{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each day of the game represents a full &quot;loop&quot;, and is broken into three separate phases: <strong><i>Prep, Cook Time and After Hours</i></strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195920/extras/prepping.gif?t=1731347012\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Prep</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During prep time, you will be able to explore around the kitchen bus, finding ingredients and preparing things (what and how much is up to you). You can also use this time to buy new items for your restaurant, such as supplies, shelving, etc...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195920/extras/cooking.gif?t=1731347012\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cooking Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Opening the restaurant allows customers to stop by and order your... delicious? food? You receive and order from a customer, try to make something resembling the order then deliver it to the plate. Click the order ticket and send them on their way! This earns you money (shotgun shells) that you can use later!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195920/extras/punching.gif?t=1731347012\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">After Hours</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is when things get spicy. Use your money to order things, clean up, and sleep. But be warned, that customer you gave food poisoning earlier? He's back, and he's gonna hit you with a stick. If only you had some way to defend yourself, but that'd leave a body and those aren't good for business. Or maybe they are...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195920/extras/grinder_throw.gif?t=1731347012\" /></p><p cla